Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.57,0:21:28.80,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰かのようになりたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.98,0:21:32.70,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}だけどなれるはずもなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.61,0:21:37.51,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いじけるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.09,0:21:41.10,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の中にいる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.42,0:21:44.67,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}もう一人の自分が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.19,0:21:50.24,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}教えてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.23,0:21:53.38,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あるがままなんかじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.44,0:21:58.24,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}きっといられないから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.93,0:22:05.01,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰もが皆悩んでもがいてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.55,0:22:12.08,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}弱音吐いたり愚痴ってみたり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.28,0:22:19.08,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そうやって毎日を過ごしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.51,0:22:25.97,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}傷つけられることに慣れた僕らは知ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.38,0:22:32.79,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}優しさとか想いだけじゃ  生きていけないことを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.07,0:22:39.10,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}だけど自分らしく　ありたいと思うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.27,0:22:47.33,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}いつだって  僕ら歩いてく
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------EDCN-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.57,0:21:28.80,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}想要像别人那样优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.98,0:21:32.70,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}也知道这不过是幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.61,0:21:37.51,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}每当遇到挫折
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.09,0:21:41.10,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}守护在心中的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.42,0:21:44.67,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}另一个自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.19,0:21:50.24,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就会这样告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.23,0:21:53.38,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}放任自己随波逐流
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.44,0:21:58.24,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}自己当然不愿这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.93,0:22:05.01,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}没有人不烦恼焦急
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.55,0:22:12.08,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}叫苦连天  牢骚不停
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.28,0:22:19.08,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就这样度过每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.51,0:22:25.97,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}对受伤已经麻木的我们没有人不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.38,0:22:32.79,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}仅仅凭着那份心里的温存  哪能在残酷的世间站稳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.07,0:22:39.10,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}尽管如此  还是想活出自己的精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.27,0:22:47.33,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}我们一起走下去  直到永远
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------TEXT-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小篝情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.61,0:02:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家里休息  基本已经平静下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡着了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还说已经开始练习走路了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.68,0:02:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到现在心情也平复了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.71,0:02:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.89,0:02:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉都这么努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  直呼你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.52,0:03:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样是不是太亲昵了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.61,0:03:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.16,0:03:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊  优
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在干嘛  都说了早上要开会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  要抓紧时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  可以跑过去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管我的  你先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.74,0:03:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  待会见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小  小幡学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打得不错嘛  小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.15,0:04:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定了  真透你当夏季大赛的准正式队员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天开始的合宿里我会好好锻炼你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好吃苦头的准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.79,0:04:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真能干  真透
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说回来  没想到和小鸟游能亲密到一起上学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好肉麻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫小幡学姐在合宿时把你这性格改过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.03,0:04:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃苦头…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.01,0:04:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长的一对一训练的机会是可遇不可求啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕  小幡学姐挺严格的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要听见那「啾啾」的脚步声就开始紧张…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.74,0:04:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这边？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:04:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道那是在告白？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.72,0:05:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.36,0:05:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幡学姐脸红了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内八字  内八字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.51,0:05:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.69,0:05:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带几条毛巾好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦汗的时候  打翻东西的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  软膏软膏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.49,0:05:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天没做梦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.53,0:05:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.69,0:05:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泪水的蓝色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸟在泪水的蓝色中飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.36,0:06:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缤纷小鸟在缤纷的天空中飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.12,0:06:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容的橙色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒的粉红色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泪水的蓝色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次飞越不同的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.73,0:06:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身上就会染上不同的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美丽的彩虹色的小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而小鸟想看更多的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.12,0:06:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颜色慢慢相互交融  渐渐浑浊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子眼瞳的颜色会变吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.48,0:06:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实没什么要紧的事  不知不觉就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.80,0:06:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉啊  这个不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿准备成怎样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好麻烦  刚刚优又发短信过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问我「全部收拾好了吗」还附上了行李清单
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是爱操心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透和小优关系真好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该算是孽缘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.89,0:07:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从幼儿园到现在了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.82,0:07:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小优虽然现在装得很正经
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前还是个很奇怪的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.12,0:07:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉总是静不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学的时候经常在上课时跑出教室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.79,0:07:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  在你正忙的时候打电话过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有关系啦  我挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后再给你发短信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.88,0:08:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被星光的群山拥抱～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.63,0:08:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  真透  呕吐袋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.47,0:08:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理经人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是吗  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.56,0:08:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认人的记性不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吐一下会舒服很多的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是不想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.09,0:08:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是顽固
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲啊  真透
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.77,0:08:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错不错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小幡  你要让她当准正式队员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:09:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不担心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们打团队合作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像不太愿意跟其他人合作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.11,0:09:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会吗  反正有理经人在  没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.97,0:09:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有理经人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  还没使出全力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.22,0:10:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了  来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.79,0:10:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然都会遇上不同的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不认识的人特别多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.79,0:10:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前那个孩子又不在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前沙耶老师说过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.32,0:10:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有人替你承受各种痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.28,0:10:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定真透的痛就是那孩子来承受的  这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.29,0:10:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听起来好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:11:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子在承受我的痛楚？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很帅气  但是听不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  之前偶尔出现的人今天也在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是个阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Comment: 0,0:00:00.92,0:00:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.52,0:11:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来给我们看看其他的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.84,0:11:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  之后再给
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.71,0:12:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个送给沙耶老师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还是这个比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  这样暖一下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部就走光了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透  真色
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.21,0:12:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧  小幡  那算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.55,0:12:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为日本男儿总希望他能强大一点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.11,0:12:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幡那个要买给男生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.52,0:12:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是给他呀  3班的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.02,0:12:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,STOP  STOP  不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来那个是给之前那个男生的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.59,0:12:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点可爱呢  小幡前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透也想要男朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  还太早了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少等升到高中再说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.57,0:12:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为真透有小鸟游呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.83,0:12:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.33,0:13:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.37,0:13:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真可以收下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.86,0:13:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尝尝看  试吃的时候觉得很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.41,0:13:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  合宿开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.24,0:13:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优睡觉磨牙太吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.42,0:13:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点睡不着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.99,0:13:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优咬牙的声音呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.64,0:13:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是伴着奇怪的节奏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.19,0:13:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.43,0:13:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.63,0:13:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什么在意的事就要说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使不是最要好的朋友吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  我也送给真透
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  颜色不同的  可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.96,0:13:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮的蓝色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.65,0:14:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.64,0:14:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  优
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.89,0:14:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊  早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚了那么多人在这里有什么有趣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.99,0:14:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  小幡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做的不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.67,0:14:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人婆居然还写情书呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不自量力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说合宿带回来的特产居然是木刀诶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.32,0:14:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.01,0:14:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  拓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.87,0:14:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  这样小幡太可怜了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确这不符合我的性格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:14:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:14:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.77,0:15:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要挂墙头展示的话我可要收钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.41,0:15:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幡前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幡前辈居然笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事根本不是能笑出来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她却笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优你不也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭的时机…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今一起度过的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.18,0:15:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后将要一起度过的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今流下的眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后将要流下的眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们两个都一样呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.06,0:15:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来了  要来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不该去做不习惯的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.22,0:16:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幡同学  明明哭出来也没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.19,0:16:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难过的话哭出来也没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.75,0:16:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过事情都已经发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是坚强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.54,0:16:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚强真是让人心痛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙耶…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:17:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘲笑小幡同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听  在嘲笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.51,0:17:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在嘲笑小幡同学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.07,0:17:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘲笑我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幡同学…大家的笑料小幡同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.12,0:17:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逞强  硬来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幡同学的心好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.16,0:17:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时小幡同学存在本身也好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.31,0:18:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿  小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.49,0:18:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝点咖啡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.15,0:18:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幡前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.88,0:18:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.11,0:18:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把你给绊倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍微扭了一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.14,0:18:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会  现在可是夏季大赛临近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真透  来扶我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.65,0:18:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.21,0:18:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.47,0:18:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呀…就算有什么难过的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.25,0:18:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也都不想怪罪到别人头上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.23,0:19:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幡前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为要是怪罪别人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.94,0:19:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就代表自己什么都没努力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得原因都在自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就会觉得自己什么都能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.18,0:19:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何时候都能奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何时候都能飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幡前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只凭我的治疗肯定不够
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.73,0:19:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找保健室的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.69,0:19:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果老师不在的话就找沙耶老师好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.47,0:19:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙耶老师就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  都算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.80,0:19:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己能行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.39,0:19:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快点回去练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.58,0:19:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.17,0:19:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是偷懒就剥夺你准正式队员的名额哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快点去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.91,0:19:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.45,0:19:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可爱的学妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸟游同学  要放糖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要两勺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.57,0:20:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.87,0:20:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.17,0:20:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.84,0:20:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我泡成黑咖啡了
